Feng Ran!

739
00:39:58,127 --> 00:39:58,847
Jing Jian.

740
00:40:01,726 --> 00:40:02,407
Jangan gelisah,

741
00:40:02,887 --> 00:40:03,887
saya lepaskan awak sekarang juga!

742
00:40:08,847 --> 00:40:09,686
Mengapa boleh begini?

743
00:40:10,367 --> 00:40:11,327
Apa jenis api rohani ini?

744
00:40:11,327 --> 00:40:11,966
Saya tak perlu lihat pun!

745
00:40:12,567 --> 00:40:13,486
