di sini?

749
00:40:25,526 --> 00:40:26,966
Dia dah tahu identiti awak?

750
00:40:28,726 --> 00:40:29,887
Awak dah tahu sejak awal lagi?

751
00:40:30,847 --> 00:40:31,847
